							<li>Mesh WiFi with parental controls: $300-500</li>
							<li>Annual monitoring software (optional): $300-1,000</li>
						</ul>
						<p>
							<strong>Medium institutions (25-100 users):</strong>
						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Business-grade router with filtering: $500-1,500</li>
							<li>Premium DNS service: $200-500/year</li>
							<li>Enterprise filtering software: $1,000-3,000/year</li>
						</ul>
						<p>
							<strong>Large institutions (100+ users):</strong>
						</p>
						<ul>
