							<li><strong>Share testimonials:</strong> Stories from affected families (with permission)</li>
							<li><strong>Invite feedback:</strong> Collaborative policy development increases buy-in</li>
							<li><strong>Start gradually:</strong> Pilot program before full rollout</li>
							<li><strong>Offer alternatives:</strong> Those who object can opt not to use institutional internet</li>
							<li><strong>Leadership example:</strong> Leaders should model healthy digital habits</li>
						</ul>
